.\" docs/man/meow-generate.1
.TH MEOW-GENERATE 1 "2025-09-19" "meowg1k" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
meow-generate \- generate any content based on input — code, text,
or docs
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B meow generate
[\fIflags\fR] [\fIarguments...\fR]
.br
.B meow g
[\fIflags\fR] [\fIarguments...\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Generate content using configured profiles and tasks. Supports all available
providers through the profile system with smart defaults and minimal configuration.
Input can be provided via stdin and/or user prompt flags.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.BR \-t ", " \-\-task " " \fINAME\fR
Run a predefined task from configuration. Tasks are defined in the
.B generate.tasks
section of config files.
.TP
.BR \-p ", " \-\-user\-prompt " " \fITEXT\fR
User prompt for generation. Can be combined with stdin for context.
.TP
.BR \-h ", " \-\-help
Show command help.

.SH CONFIGURATION
Uses the profile system defined in
.BR meow\-config (5).
Profiles specify provider, model, and other settings with smart defaults.

Tasks can override the default profile and add custom prompts:

.nf
generate:
  default:
    profile: "fast"
  tasks:
    review:
      profile: "smart"
      userPrompt: "Review this code thoroughly"
.fi
\fB--model\fR is ignored. Use \fB--llama-base-url\fR to connect.
.SH CONFIGURATION
Configuration files are read with the following precedence:
.IP "1." 3
Project: \fB./.meowg1k/config.yaml\fR
.SH EXAMPLES
Use a predefined task:
.br
.B cat main.go | meow generate \-t review
.PP
Direct prompt with stdin:
.br
.B cat service.py | meow generate \-p "Add comprehensive error handling"
.PP
Simple prompt without stdin:
.br
.B echo "Create a REST API" | meow generate \-p "Write Go code"
.PP
Project-specific task:
.br
.B cat auth.go | meow generate \-t security

.SH ENVIRONMENT
Providers use these environment variables for API keys:
.TP
.B MEOW_GEMINI_API_KEY
API key for Gemini provider.
.TP
.B MEOW_OPENAI_API_KEY
API key for OpenAI provider.
.TP
.B MEOW_OPENROUTER_API_KEY
API key for OpenRouter provider.
.TP
.B MEOW_NEBIUS_API_KEY
API key for Nebius provider.
.TP
.B MEOW_ANTHROPIC_API_KEY
API key for Anthropic provider.
.TP
.B MEOW_VOYAGE_API_KEY
API key for Voyage AI provider (embeddings only).
.TP
.B MEOW_LLAMA_API_KEY
Optional API key for llama provider.
.TP
.B MEOW_OPENAI_COMPATIBLE_API_KEY
API key for OpenAI-compatible providers.

.SH EXIT STATUS
Returns 0 on success, non-zero on error.

.SH SEE ALSO
.BR meow (1),
.BR meow\-version (1),
.BR meow\-config (5),
.BR meow\-security (7)
